{"tid":687543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"橋上放生鯽魚 橋底村民狂撈「海鮮餐」","createTime":"2018-06-02T11:02:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T12:00:12.000Z","uid":1886,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b1780f54712ba8599e16712916f61fe5bcf4c003","tid":687543,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:02:24.000Z","msg":"「不撈而獲」賦予新解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！河北保定近日有民眾在橋上放生鯽魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，沒想到橋下就是村民平日的捕魚點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，橋下就一桶一桶的狂撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，收獲十分豐富<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，回家準備一頓海鮮餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180601/large/1527862019_89d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180601%2Flarge%2F1527862019_89d8.jpg&h=063fdaec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180602/58264634\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180602%2F58264634&d=mrgUYd5Ed7UwA6vG9LKaBZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=8a9fb75e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180602%2F58264634&h=09ea3499\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180602/58264634</a></div>"},{"pid":"3443f82900baba8bb0e10670a06f50ef2413419c","tid":687543,"uid":1886,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:02:47.000Z","msg":"村民指，上周六（5月26日）有一些外地人入村在橋上放生還沒搞清楚，原來該處就是村民在橋下捕魚。他說：「他們在橋上放，人們就在河道裏撈，都是一桶一桶撈的，本來那兒就是打魚的，他們還在那放生，魚剛下他們就撈上來了。」<br />\n<br />\n網民揶揄：「這就是所謂的生態平衡吧！」「放生=殺生」、「這不挺好嘛，放生的也高興，捕魚的也高興，一條魚讓兩個人都得到了滿足。」"},{"pid":"f9e01309d048e2edad085e99e0ac693c8370c63a","tid":687543,"uid":1221,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:17:03.000Z","msg":"「 沒事兒 沒事兒 」"},{"pid":"69a3ee25e70a2d4d2ea916e15fc613a750f810ee","tid":687543,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:19:29.000Z","msg":"放生 = on9"},{"pid":"f31dc0f1d48d8a1fdd085bda6253d8bdcee20a21","tid":687543,"uid":33357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:32:57.000Z","msg":"又黎 班垃圾幾時先知放生係殺生?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b9aa59a5a2df5fe15a1cede453f36e00338ac24","tid":687543,"uid":129235,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:44:37.000Z","msg":"撈完囉返上橋上邊賣<br />\nd人又買來放生<br />\n無限循環，fat fat <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965c7adeeae525979950d565bce757025ff97d0f","tid":687543,"uid":83217,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:47:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hahatai.com/sites/default/files/u1031/5_160.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hahatai.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fu1031%2F5_160.jpg&h=c3cde66e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b60896d0faf771b89bfd27f75bb2fe768e81483d","tid":687543,"uid":178110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:50:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4286bfa08d9790774bdc1aca20e75402c5755462","tid":687543,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b60896d0faf771b89bfd27f75bb2fe768e81483d","tid":687543,"uid":178110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"965c7adeeae525979950d565bce757025ff97d0f","tid":687543,"uid":83217,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:47:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hahatai.com/sites/default/files/u1031/5_160.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ha